      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"896 characters\">Attended Industry Events<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"896 characters\">I regularly attended cybersecurity meetups and college-hosted tech talks. These events helped me understand real-world security tools and trends, not just theory.<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"896 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"896 characters\">Built Practical Skills Outside Class<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"896 characters\">I practiced on platforms like TryHackMe and worked on small personal labs. This gave me hands-on experience that I could confidently talk about in interviews.<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"896 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"896 characters\">Optimized My Resume for ATS<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"896 characters\">I updated my resume to include keywords from job descriptions (e.g., SIEM, vulnerability scanning, incident response). This helped my resume pass automated screenings.<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"896 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
